title: Hardin County newspaper that focused on corruption will be digitally archived
text:
Published By: Beaumont Enterprise: Communities - Today 
Copies of The Pine Needle, a weekly newspaper published from 1964-1968, will be sent to the university in Denton to be scanned and archived ...
